node.text: “Like so many of us, we’ve been reflecting and thinking through how we want to show up for our associates and our communities and be a force for change. Now, we’re taking action.” Hear from Samara Tuchband, Head of our Diversity and Inclusion Council and VP of Merchandising for our sister brand @crateandbarrel speak about our immediate next steps to support diversity and the Black Lives Matter movement.
